num::<impl u8>::wrapping_sub.doc:
Wrapping (modular) subtraction. Computes `self - rhs`,
 wrapping around at the boundary of the type.

 # Examples

 ```
 ```

option::Option: Unknown([Downcast(VariantIdx(1, ThreadLocalIndex)), Field(0, Ty { id: 446, kind: RigidTy(Tuple([Ty { id: 447, kind: RigidTy(Ref(Region { kind: ReErased }, Ty { id: 46, kind: RigidTy(Uint(U8)) }, Not)) }, Ty { id: 419, kind: RigidTy(Ref(Region { kind: ReErased }, Ty { id: 423, kind: RigidTy(Slice(Ty { id: 46, kind: RigidTy(Uint(U8)) })) }, Not)) }])) }), Field(0, Ty { id: 447, kind: RigidTy(Ref(Region { kind: ReErased }, Ty { id: 46, kind: RigidTy(Uint(U8)) }, Not)) })])

Unknown([Downcast(VariantIdx(1, ThreadLocalIndex)), Field(0, Ty { id: 446, kind: RigidTy(Tuple([Ty { id: 447, kind: RigidTy(Ref(Region { kind: ReErased }, Ty { id: 46, kind: RigidTy(Uint(U8)) }, Not)) }, Ty { id: 419, kind: RigidTy(Ref(Region { kind: ReErased }, Ty { id: 423, kind: RigidTy(Slice(Ty { id: 46, kind: RigidTy(Uint(U8)) })) }, Not)) }])) }), Field(1, Ty { id: 419, kind: RigidTy(Ref(Region { kind: ReErased }, Ty { id: 423, kind: RigidTy(Slice(Ty { id: 46, kind: RigidTy(Uint(U8)) })) }, Not)) })])
